title: Kamal Gurbanov
text:
Kamal Gurbanov (; born on 12 July 1995) is an <a href="Azerbaijan">Azerbaijan</a>i <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="Defender%20%28association%20football%29%23Full-back">Right-back</a> who plays for <a href="Sabail%20FK">Sabail</a> in the <a href="Azerbaijan%20Premier%20League">Azerbaijan Premier League</a>.
Club career.
On 9 August 2015, Gurbanov made his debut in the <a href="Azerbaijan%20Premier%20League">Azerbaijan Premier League</a> for <a href="Neft%C3%A7i%20PFK">Neftçi Baku</a> match against <a href="Kapaz%20PFK">Kapaz</a>.
